apifeatureusage-desc:
{{desc|name=Api Feature Usage|url=https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:ApiFeatureUsage}}

See definition of [[w:User agent|user agent]] on Wikipedia.
apifeatureusage-elasticsearch-error:
Used to wrap an Elasticsearch error when reporting it up the stack.

Parameters:
* $1 - Error message from Elasticsearch.
apifeatureusage-legend: Used as a fieldset legend on [[Special:ApiFeatureUsage]].
apifeatureusage-column-feature:
Column header for the table containing the output. Cells in the "Feature" column contain the name of the feature the usage of which is counted. 

{{Identical|Feature}}
apifeatureusage-column-date:
Column header for output table. Dates in the column are in the UTC timezone, formatted as Y-m-d (similar to ISO 8601 format).

{{Identical|Date}}
apifeatureusage-column-uses:
Column header for the table containing the output. Cells in "Uses" column contain the number of occurrences of the event.

{{Identical|Use}}
